# Blog Module Guide

## Blog Posts
### Endpoints
- List posts: `GET /api/blog/posts`
- Create post: `POST /api/blog/posts`
- Get post: `GET /api/blog/posts/{post_slug_or_id}`
- Update post: `PUT/PATCH /api/blog/posts/{post_id}`
- Delete post: `DELETE /api/blog/posts/{post_id}`
- Increment view: `POST /api/blog/posts/{post_id}/increment-view`

### Query Parameters
- `category`: Filter by category (slug or ID)
- `author`: Filter by author (slug or ID)
- `tag`: Filter by tag (slug or ID)
- `status`: Filter by status
- `featured`: Filter featured posts
- `sort`: Sort order (e.g., `-published_at`, `title`)
- `per_page`: Items per page

## Blog Categories
### Endpoints
- List categories: `GET /api/blog/categories`
- Create category: `POST /api/blog/categories`
- Get category: `GET /api/blog/categories/{category_slug_or_id}`
- Update category: `PUT/PATCH /api/blog/categories/{category_id}`
- Delete category: `DELETE /api/blog/categories/{category_id}`

### Query Parameters
- `hierarchical`: Get nested structure (boolean)

